              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-lg p-6">
              <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">尝试 FreeModel</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-3">免费额度 + 国内直连，通过一个 OpenAI 兼容接口访问 50+ 模型。</p>
              <a href="https://freemodel.dev/invite/FRE-7a3b6220" class="text-sm text-blue-600 hover:underline break-all">freemodel.dev/invite/FRE-7a3b6220</a>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-gray-100 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 text-center">
